<title>Krishna Solar</title>

<style>

body{
font-family: Arial;
margin:0;
padding:0;
background:#f4f4f4;
}

header{
background:#0a8f2a;
color:white;
padding:20px;
text-align:center;
}

nav{
background:#333;
padding:10px;
text-align:center;
}

nav a{
color:white;
